  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      We wish to study sleep architecture in patients with chronic orthostatic intolerance. We will
      test the null hypothesis that there is no difference in time during the various phases of
      sleep between patients and healthy control subjects.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
